Transform your browser into a chilling Fortnite experience with the Fortnite Haunted Hush Live Wallpaper, where eerie visuals and spooky vibes take over your new tab.

This live wallpaper brings to life the mysterious and haunting Fortnite skin, Haunted Hush. As she glides across your screen, you’ll be immersed in a world of darkness, with ghostly effects and chilling undertones. Haunted Hush's ethereal presence will make every new tab a mysterious adventure in the Fortnite universe.

Key Features
👻 Haunted Hush Live Wallpaper: Watch as the spooky Fortnite character, Haunted Hush, comes alive with captivating animations and eerie effects.
🔍 Integrated Search Bar: Quickly search the web with your preferred search engine from your new tab.
🕒 Clock and Date: Stay up-to-date with an integrated clock and date display.
📌 Customizable Shortcuts: Add or remove shortcuts to access your favorite websites effortlessly.
⚙️ Extension Settings: Easily manage or remove the extension via the settings menu in the bottom-left corner.
With the Fortnite Haunted Hush Live Wallpaper, your browser will feel like a haunted space, bringing Fortnite’s dark side to life right before your eyes.
